              ## About the Author

              My name is Gavin Morrice. I describe myself as an *armchair philosopher*
              because I do most of my thinking from home, reflecting on my observations of
               the world I experience around me&mdash;I'm not an "academic".

              I aim to gain a better understanding of the world and our place in it&mdash;
              a journey which has dragged me in many different directions, including
              writing, art, science, philosophy, and business.

              **The Great Pantomime is my first book.**

    section
