              ## What is The Great Pantomime

              The Great Pantomime is a non-fiction book that attempts to describe the
              world we humans have created for ourselves, and how far we've departed from
              our natural roots.

              Much of what we seek in life is actually a distraction from the things we
              really need. This book aims to answer why.


